    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You must drive a whole night with the-- with the train.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Russia, you could not move-- I don't know about now, but before without a [NON-ENGLISH].",
